title: Chicago Cubs take on New York Mets in Game 3 Monday evening
text:
Chicago Cubs take on New York Mets in Game 3 Monday evening 
By Kayla Crandall -21Alive October 20, 2015 Updated Oct 20, 2015 at 7:08 PM EDT 
CHICAGO (21Alive) -- As tomorrow, Oct. 21, 2015, marks the day that Marty McFly travels to save his kids in "Back to the Future Part II", the Chicago Cubs take on the New York Mets Tuesday evening. 
This is Game 3, and 21Alive's Dean Pantazi made the trip to Wrigley Field to scope out the fans and even found some Fort Wayne natives at the game.
